      <div class="msgContentFrame">Let me rephrase that, for the cost of Shards only.  This is assuming you make every synth, but even if you don't, you won't lose to much. <br /> <br />What you need: <br />Weathered Doming Hammer <br />3 Copper Nuggets (per synth) <br />11 Earth Shards (6 and 5 per each synth) <br />1 Wind Shard (per synth) <br /> <br /> <br />NPCs Who Sell Copper Nuggets (400g a piece): <br />Uldah - Doesdornn - Sapphire Avenue Exchange <br />Uldah - Pamisolaux - Goldsmith Guild <br /> <br />Gridania - Gagaulu - Rosewood Stalls <br />Gridania - Ahldiyrn - Ebony Stalls <br /> <br />Limsa Lominsa - Teteu - West Hawker's Alley (Lower Decks) <br />Limsa Lominsa - Smydhaemr - Blacksmith / Armorer Guild (Upper Decks) <br /> <br /> <br />What to create: <br />Copper Square (creates 12) <br />6 x Earth Shard <br />3 x Copper Nuggets <br /> <br />Copper Toes (creates 1) <br />5 x Earth Shard <br />1 x Wind Shard <br />2 Copper Squares <br /> <br /> <br />The Breakdown: <br />Basically start out with 12 Nuggets for 4800g.  Make Copper Squares first, then once those are done, start making Copper Toes.  If you succeed on every synth, you should make a total of 24 Toes, which sell back to the vendor for 4800g exactly.  This is the only Synth Recipe I've found that can get you up to 10 easily for only the cost of shards (assuming you don't fail any). <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct  8th 2010  7:51pm by Vidffxiv </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /></div></div>
